   318	| T-02-02 | Denial of Service / wrong output | Chunk(mz,width) on empty/single-point/all-equal/non-monotonic m/z | mitigate | Window chunker never emits length-1 chunk, always emits residual, emits nothing for empty; explicit ArgumentException on non-monotonic; empty/all-equal/single-point/guard unit tests (Task 1) |
