   321	| T-02-05 | Tampering (read path) | decoder on reference null markers | mitigate | Reference null-decode unit tests ([None, absolute, delta], [None, None]) (Task 1) so reference/Phase-4 files read correctly |
   322	| T-02-SC | Tampering | npm/pip/cargo installs | mitigate | No package installs in this phase (RESEARCH Package Legitimacy Audit: none) — gate is a no-op |
   323	</threat_model>
